      "claimType": "story-chapter",
      "claimTextEn": "Qaytbay’s foundation joined a mosque-madrasa and royal mausoleum with charitable and residential components. Its carved stone dome, minaret, striped masonry, colored glass, and compact interior represent late Mamluk craftsmanship. The place must be read within the living Qarafa rather than as an isolated monument.",
